data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Potomac Shores community! This property boasts a coastal bungalow style with a main floor owners' suite, high ceilings, and inviting outdoor living areas. Admire the beautiful curb appeal with a two-tone inlay concrete driveway and cozy covered front porch. Inside, enjoy wide plank hardwood floors, a spacious office, and a grand room with 14-foot ceilings and a gas fireplace. The chef's kitchen features a large center island and upgraded appliances, while the main floor suite offers a spa-like bath with a jetted soaking tub. The finished lower level includes a rec room with a wet bar, bedroom, full bathroom, and plenty of room to add additional bedrooms or flex space. Outside, the upgraded deck and flagstone patio provide exceptional outdoor living spaces, perfect for entertaining or relaxation. Plus, the HOA includes high-speed internet, trash, and access to world-class amenities such as state-of-the-art fitness facilities, a Jack Nicklaus Signature Public Golf Course, swimming pools, social facilities, miles of walking trails, and more. With top-notch amenities and nearby schools, this home in Potomac Shores offers a wonderful combination of luxury and community living.Take the VRE train (coming soon est ..2025) to Washington DC . Professional Pictures coming soon!
